                            <text>must amend the Register so that the component parties recorded in the Register are the same as those recorded in the declaration made to the Electoral Commission; and</text>
                          </para>
                        </label-para>
                        <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                          <para>
                            <text>must, immediately after amending the Register under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">paragraph (a)</citation></changeable>, publish in the <emphasis style="italic">Gazette</emphasis> a notice of the amendment made under that paragraph.</text>
