                          </para>
                        </label-para>
                        <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                          <para>
                            <text>that copy is to be treated for all purposes as the copy forwarded to the Clerk of the House of Representatives under section 185(1).</text>
